title: Plastics - Welcome Plastics
description:
Plastics - Welcome Plastics (1979)

Crazy Japanese electro-pop with silly, English nonsensical lyrics. A must-hear for every fan of Devo, B52&#039;s and other electro-goodness. I&#039;m putting it up here because I&#039;ve spent a long, long time looking for it and I don&#039;t think I&#039;m the only one.

My upstream isn&#039;t really impressive, but I&#039;ll seed as long as possible - hopefully someone with a better connection will help out at some point.

Enjoy! ;)
